metadata.author: Purple Rocket Podcast
metadata.description: Bo is a homeschooler who's just getting over his obsessive dinosaur phase. But when his parents send him to a dinosaur summer camp in the middle of the jungle his world is turned upside down. At Camp Dino you don't dig for fake fossils or sit through boring classes, you RAISE your own dinosaur from an egg. Join Bo and his friends for an unforgettable adventure into the world of dinosaurs!
